</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Auto-genererede filer</bold>: Nogle builds genererer <computeroutput>*.g.cs</computeroutput> i stedet for <computeroutput>*.g.i.cs</computeroutput> – det er OK.</para>
